Ray Baker (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Baker_(actor) 0 Ray Baker (born July 9, 1948) is an American theater, television and film actor. Baker was born in Omaha, Nebraska. He is a long time character actor with over 100 credits on television and film alone. Baker is credited either as Ray or Raymond.
